originalText.text: Marvina is VERY unprofessional with answering simple questions like when was the last time that he ate and had his milk so I won't over feed him or not feed him when I'm supposed to. She kept calling and screaming at me over the phone and even tried to threaten me over the same question I asked LITERALLY EVERYDAY. I honestly think that she was high because not only did that happen but my less than 1 year old son at that time came home acting like he didn't eat and have his milk all day. I do not recommend this daycare at all. I trusted her because she is from the same church I used to go to and knew my family but obviously that was a mistake but never again will I be making that same mistake and I truly hope no one else does too. Her attitude and mouth is absolutely disgusting and I don't trust her with my child or anyone else's child because of it. I'm just being honest. She made me very very very disappointed in her.
